; Test account directive eval sub-directive
; Exercise the eval keyword within an account directive

account Expenses:Food
    eval 1 + 1

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Test                  Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
end test
